### Me (requer cookie access_token do login; valida autenticação)
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Refresh (gera novo par de tokens via cookie refresh_token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/refresh
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Logout (revoga refresh atual e limpa cookies)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
